                            <comment id="17476966" author="davsclaus" created="Mon, 17 Jan 2022 06:06:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;What version of Camel do you use, and can you make an example that can reproduce this issue?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17477037" author="cgp" created="Mon, 17 Jan 2022 08:54:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We are using Camel K 1.7.0 which is using Camel 3.12.0. Our server is private and the code below is the snippet of the client connecting to it&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
fromF(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;ahc-wss:&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;private&lt;/span&gt;-server-url&amp;amp;bridgeErrorHandler=&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&amp;amp;sendMessageOnError=&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;  .filter(exchange -&amp;gt; exchange.getIn().getBody() != &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;)
  .toF(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;kafka:%s?brokers=%s&amp;amp;groupId=%s&amp;amp;bridgeErrorHandler=&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, kafkaTopic, kafkaBrokers, kafkaGroupId);&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17477125" author="davsclaus" created="Mon, 17 Jan 2022 11:08:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;You are welcome to attempt to fix this and send a PR&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
